            <div>
               <head>V.</head>
               <p>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
O Blessed God who art rich in <normalised orig="mercie" auto="true">mercy</normalised> and <lb/>
compassion, take care of all states of Men <lb/>
and Women in the Christian Church, the <lb/>
Nobility and Gentry, Magistrates and Judges, <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <fw type="pageNum">C 2</fw>
                  <pb n="18"/>
                  <lb/>
Advocates and Physicians, Merchants and <lb/>
Artificers, <normalised orig="Husbandmen" auto="true">Husbandman</normalised> and Tradesmen, the <lb/>
