                  <lb/>
Lord have mercy upon us. <lb/>
Christ have mercy upon us. <lb/>
Lord have mercy upon us. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
FOr if thou Lord wilt be extreme to <normalised orig="marke" auto="true">mark</normalised> <lb/>
