            <div>
               <head>VII.</head>
               <p>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
BE a guide to the travellers, a star and a <lb/>
port to Mariners, the comfort and strength <lb/>
of Miners and Gallislaves. Pity good God, <lb/>
all Gentlemen that are fallen into poverty and <lb/>
                  <pb n="19"/>
                  <lb/>
