thy <normalised orig="councell" auto="true">council</normalised>, and after that receive us with thy <lb/>
glory through Jesus Christ our Lord. Amen. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
O <normalised orig="Eternall" auto="true">Eternal</normalised> God thou <normalised orig="fountaine" auto="true">fountain</normalised> of life and <lb/>
