old age: they shall be fat and flourishing. <lb/>
To <normalised orig="shew" auto="true">show</normalised> that the Lord is upright: he is <lb/>
our rock, and there is no <normalised orig="unrighteousnesse" auto="true">unrighteousness</normalised> in <lb/>
