Holy Spirit; that we may love thee and <normalised orig="feare" auto="true">fear</normalised> <lb/>
thee, and by repentance and charity may enter <lb/>
into thy favour, and dwell there by a holy <lb/>
perseverance all our <normalised orig="daies" auto="true">days</normalised>, through Jesus <lb/>
Christ our Lord. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
GRacious Father give thy servant leave to <lb/>
rely upon thy glorious promises: thou <lb/>
<normalised orig="hast" auto="true">have</normalised> commanded us to call upon thee in our <lb/>
