spirit, may for ever obey thy heavenly calling: <lb/>
that we may not be <normalised orig="onely" auto="true">only</normalised> hearers of the word <lb/>
of life, but doers also of good <normalised orig="workes" auto="true">works</normalised>, keeping <lb/>
faith and a good conscience, living an unblameable <lb/>
life, usefully and charitably, religiously and <lb/>
