<normalised orig="sitteth" auto="true">sits</normalised> on the right hand of God the Father <lb/>
Almighty * From thence he shall come to <lb/>
judge the <normalised orig="quicke" auto="true">quick</normalised> and the Dead. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
* I believe in the holy Ghost * The holy <lb/>
<normalised orig="Catholick" auto="true">Catholic</normalised> Church, the communion of Saints <lb/>
