from violent pains and passions, <lb/>
from all <notvariant>undecency</notvariant> of Comportment and <notvariant>unquietness</notvariant> <lb/>
of Spirit, from impatience and despair, <lb/>
from doing any thing that is criminal, <lb/>
or feeling any thing that is intolerable. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
BLess me, even me, O my Father, and grant <lb/>
