<normalised orig="confesse" auto="true">confess</normalised> our sins every day, and yet every day <lb/>
sin <normalised orig="aginst" auto="true">against</normalised> thee; and we pray unto thee for all <lb/>
the blessings that we <normalised orig="neede" auto="true">need</normalised>, and thou <normalised orig="givest" auto="true">give</normalised> us <lb/>
all that we pray for and much more; but yet <lb/>
we regard thee not, but every day have new <lb/>
matter of shame and sorrow. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
Lord have mercy upon us. <lb/>
Christ have mercy upon us. <lb/>
Lord have mercy upon us. <lb/>
                  <lb/>
