mercy: thou art good and gracious, infinitely <lb/>
gracious, essentially good, and <normalised orig="delightest" auto="true">delight</normalised> in <lb/>
<normalised orig="shewing" auto="true">showing</normalised> mercy to them that call upon thee, &amp; <lb/>
put their trust in thee: O dear God I remember <lb/>
that thou didst <normalised orig="releive" auto="true">relieve</normalised> the sorrows of thy <lb/>
